// Choices Demo - Branching Narrative

You stand at a crossroads in the forest.

* [Go left]
    You walk down the left path and find a beautiful waterfall.
    -> waterfall
* [Go right]
    You take the right path and discover an ancient cave.
    -> cave
* [Go back]
    You decide to return home. Sometimes safety is the best choice.
    -> home

=== waterfall ===
The waterfall cascades down into a crystal-clear pool.

* [Drink the water]
    The water is refreshing and pure. You feel energized!
    -> ending
* [Continue walking]
    You follow the stream downstream.
    -> ending

=== cave ===
The cave entrance is dark and mysterious.

* [Enter the cave]
    You bravely step into the darkness...
    Inside, you find ancient paintings on the walls!
    -> ending
* [Walk away]
    You decide not to risk it and continue your journey.
    -> ending

=== home ===
You arrive safely back home.
-> ending

=== ending ===
Your adventure comes to an end.

THE END
